{"tid":827787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老再現] 劉小麗倘被DQ 馮檢基稱會考慮參選：我勝算高","createTime":"2018-09-19T07:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T07:47:09.000Z","uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c14d40aa2e815731796fdb6607fee992d0e0d1f5","tid":827787,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"九龍西補選將於提名期下周二展開，民協前成員馮檢基表示，獲民主派一致推舉的劉小麗倘可入閘，他便不會參選，惟劉倘未能入閘，他則會考慮參選。<br />\n<br />\n馮強調，去年四名民主派人士被DQ的個案與梁游宣誓案有不同，「罪不至死，被DQ不合理，對我嚟講佢（劉）今日仍然係議員嚟，再選返我睇唔到點解要競爭同一個位」，形容是「同路人的道德」，重申從無反對劉有優先參選權。<br />\n<br />\n他又重申，初選是團結同路人的最佳方法，他反對劉小麗使用特權欽點工黨李卓人作替代方案，「呢個係大佬文化復興」，令小政黨或其他民主派人士無機會參選，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>又強調若自己參選，「我覺得自己有勝算，而且勝算係高。」 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180919/58699721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180919%2F58699721&d=vWTFKYeVB2iqjjbcuzELvBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=15db4ed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180919%2F58699721&h=997ad545\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180919/58699721</a>"},{"pid":"5f0aba13ac0b599e097f1acf971ade8f6412825a","tid":827787,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:47:09.000Z","msg":"劉小麗呢d都算，比廢民呢個廢老上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}